        "subject": "LU-12288 lnet: Properly account for preferred peer NI",
        "message": "LU-12288 lnet: Properly account for preferred peer NI\n\nA peer NI can be preferred for use by local NIs, but the peer NI\nselection algorithm does not properly track the preferred status of\nthe initial lpni selected on the first loop iteration. This can break\nthe round-robin selection.\n\nHPE-bug-id: LUS-9056\nSigned-off-by: Chris Horn <chris.horn@hpe.com>\nChange-Id: I19d6b6b8295eff6f7fcb5d51e31c29e5c7386f3a\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
